<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 02:00:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>激光束无需化学修饰即可构建细胞样蛋白质网络</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/laser-beam-builds-cell-like-protein-networks-without-chemical-modification</link><description>蛋白质纤维网络在活细胞中发挥着重要作用。为了了解这些网络的动态行为，需要模型网络来进行体外研究。然而，事实证明，制造与细胞中类似的蛋白质网络很困难，因为当前的方法可能会影响这些蛋白质的生物功能，最终影响我们对任何发现的理解。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/laser-beam-builds-cell-like-protein-networks-without-chemical-modification3.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 02:00:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/laser-beam-builds-cell-like-protein-networks-without-chemical-modification</guid></item><item><title>组装成液滴的酶可以加速细胞反应</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/enzymes-that-assemble-into-droplets-can-speed-up-cellular-reactions</link><description>在过去的十年中，生物学家发现细胞用来保持其内容物组织的一种策略是一种称为相分离的现象。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/enzymes-that-assemble-into-droplets-can-speed-up-cellular-reactions2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 01:45:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/enzymes-that-assemble-into-droplets-can-speed-up-cellular-reactions</guid></item><item><title>人类 HFpEF 的严重肥胖改变了收缩蛋白的功能和组织</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/severe-obesity-in-human-hfpef-alters-contractile-protein-function-and-organization</link><description>射血分数保留的心力衰竭（HFpEF）导致大量的发病率和死亡率，并且有效的治疗方法很少。随着时间的推移，其表型发生了变化，病态肥胖和代谢缺陷取代了高血压和心脏肥大。我们发现，与肥胖程度较低的 HFpEF 和伴或不伴肥胖的非失败 (NF) 对照相比，严重肥胖和 HFpEF 患者的心肌细胞收缩储备非常低，包括钙和长度刺激的张力、功率和肌球蛋白激活降低，但与晚期 HF 和射血分数降低的患者相似。 HFpEF 患者的肌细胞缺陷与体重指数和运动血流动力学相关，但与 NF 无关，并且在体重减轻后似乎可逆。肌钙蛋白 I 苏氨酸 181 磷酸化增加仅发生在肥胖性心力衰竭中，导致肌节功能障碍。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/severe-obesity-in-human-hfpef-alters-contractile-protein-function-and-organization.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 01:30:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/severe-obesity-in-human-hfpef-alters-contractile-protein-function-and-organization</guid></item><item><title>集成管道 PhageHost，用于使用蛋白质语言模型发现噬菌体尾部纤维并准确预测肺炎克雷伯氏菌宿主</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/an-ensemble-pipeline-phagehost-for-phage-tail-fiber-discovery-and-accurate-klebsiella-pneumoniae-host-prediction-using-protein-language-models</link><description>吴等人。呈现一个集成管道， &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/an-ensemble-pipeline-phagehost-for-phage-tail-fiber-discovery-and-accurate-klebsiella-pneumoniae-host-prediction-using-protein-language-models.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 01:15:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/an-ensemble-pipeline-phagehost-for-phage-tail-fiber-discovery-and-accurate-klebsiella-pneumoniae-host-prediction-using-protein-language-models</guid></item><item><title>人工智能“超级抗原”疫苗可以预防整个病毒家族</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/ai-super-antigen-vaccine-could-protect-against-whole-families-of-viruses</link><description>具有开创性的&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-super-antigen-vaccine-could-protect-against-whole-families-of-viruses.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 01:00:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/ai-super-antigen-vaccine-could-protect-against-whole-families-of-viruses</guid></item><item><title>罗宾·汉森（第 2 部分）：社会科学还是伪装的极端主义政治？！</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/robin-hanson-part-2-social-science-or-extremist-politics-in-disguise</link><description>&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/robin-hanson-part-2-social-science-or-extremist-politics-in-disguise.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 00:45:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/robin-hanson-part-2-social-science-or-extremist-politics-in-disguise</guid></item><item><title>为什么能量会随着年龄的增长而减弱：膜脂缺失可能会破坏线粒体的稳定性</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/why-energy-fades-with-age-missing-membrane-lipid-may-destabilize-mitochondria</link><description>为什么细胞会衰老——为什么我们会随着年龄的增长而失去精力和活力？这个问题是现代生物医学的核心挑战之一。重点特别放在线粒体上，线粒体是一种微小的细胞器，长期以来被认为是细胞的动力室，但现在被理解为动态控制中心，它不仅产生能量，还协调细胞通讯、适应以及许多生命必需的过程。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/why-energy-fades-with-age-missing-membrane-lipid-may-destabilize-mitochondria.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 00:30:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/why-energy-fades-with-age-missing-membrane-lipid-may-destabilize-mitochondria</guid></item><item><title>海马 CA1 中心保护过去的知识</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/hippocampal-ca1-hub-safeguards-past-knowledge</link><description>新的研究发现了一种海马记忆交换机，可以重复使用细胞而不会删除旧的记忆。&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/hippocampal-ca1-hub-safeguards-past-knowledge.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 00:15:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/hippocampal-ca1-hub-safeguards-past-knowledge</guid></item><item><title>微软声称新的量子芯片比以前好 1000 倍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/microsoft-claims-new-quantum-chip-1000-times-better-than-before</link><description>量子计算的核心是量子位，它有望解决当今机器无法解决的问题，但众所周知，量子位非常脆弱且不稳定。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/microsoft-claims-new-quantum-chip-1000-times-better-than-before2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Jun 2026 00:00:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/microsoft-claims-new-quantum-chip-1000-times-better-than-before</guid></item><item><title>科学家首次精确编辑人类胚胎基因</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/in-a-first-scientists-precisely-edit-human-embryo-genes</link><description>研究人员依赖于一种较新的基因编辑技术，该技术可能使胚胎工程成为可能，这一前景长期以来一直令生物伦理学家感到震惊。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/in-a-first-scientists-precisely-edit-human-embryo-genes.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 23:45:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/06/in-a-first-scientists-precisely-edit-human-embryo-genes</guid></item></channel></rss>